entry.title: As Israel's Left Suffers Defeat, So Does Two-State Solution
entry.content: The ascendancy of ultranationalist and religious parties in Israel reflects a decline in support for a Jewish and Palestinian state side by side.

entry.title: Russian Oligarch Seizes 400,000 Acres of Ukrainian Farmland, Owners Say
entry.content: The family company of a Putin ally and former Russian agriculture minister has become one of the biggest farm operators in Ukraine.

entry.title: Putin Grips Economy Tighter to Supply Russian War Machine
entry.content: Russia has commandeered private enterprise to keep the military armed in fight against Ukraine but faces labor and tech shortages.
